# ShadPs4Manager

> Professional PS4 Package Management Suite

[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-GPL--3.0-blue.svg)](LICENSE)
[![Platform](https://img.shields.io/badge/platform-Linux%20%7C%20Windows%20%7C%20macOS-lightgrey.svg)]()
[![Qt](https://img.shields.io/badge/Qt-6.2%2B-green.svg)](https://www.qt.io/)

A comprehensive toolkit for extracting, organizing, and managing PS4 PKG files. Built with Qt6 and modern C++.

## 🎮 Three Powerful Applications

### 1. ShadPs4 Manager GUI (3.8 MB)
The main application with a complete graphical interface for managing PS4 packages.

**Features:**
- Visual game library with cover art
- Batch PKG extraction
- IGDB metadata integration
- Update and DLC management
- Registration system with 10-game trial
- Real-time extraction progress

[📖 Documentation](docs/manager-gui/README.md) | [🔨 Build Instructions](docs/manager-gui/BUILD.md)

### 2. PKG Extractor CLI (3.0 MB)
Command-line tool for automated PKG extraction.

**Features:**
- Fast command-line extraction
- Scriptable and automatable
- Verbose output mode
- No GUI dependencies

[📖 Documentation](docs/pkg-extractor/README.md) | [🔨 Build Instructions](docs/pkg-extractor/BUILD.md)

```bash
shadps4-pkg-extractor game.pkg /output/dir --verbose
```

### 3. Unlock Code Generator (85 KB)
Admin tool for generating license keys (administrators only).

**Features:**
- Generate unlock codes from System IDs
- Encrypted customer email storage
- Generation history tracking
- Persistent record keeping

[📖 Documentation](docs/unlock-generator/README.md) | [🔨 Build Instructions](docs/unlock-generator/BUILD.md)

## 🚀 Quick Start

### Download

Download the latest release for your platform:

**Latest Release**: [v1.0.1](https://github.com/CrownParkComputing/ShadPs4Manager/releases/latest)

- 🐧 **Linux**: `shadps4-manager-linux-x64-v1.0.1.tar.gz`
- 🪟 **Windows**: `shadps4-manager-windows-x64-v1.0.1.zip`
- 🍎 **macOS**: `shadps4-manager-macos-universal-v1.0.1.dmg`

### Installation

**Linux:**
```bash
tar -xzf shadps4-manager-linux-x64-v1.0.1.tar.gz
cd shadps4-manager
chmod +x shadps4-manager-gui
./shadps4-manager-gui
```

**Windows:**
1. Extract ZIP file
2. Double-click `shadps4-manager-gui.exe`

**macOS:**
1. Open DMG file
2. Drag to Applications folder
3. Right-click → Open (first time only)

### Build from Source

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/CrownParkComputing/ShadPs4Manager.git
cd ShadPs4Manager

# Initialize submodules
git submodule update --init --recursive

# Quick build
./build.sh

# Executables in build/bin/
ls -lh build/bin/
```

See [BUILD.md](BUILD.md) for detailed build instructions.

