## 🔨 Building

### Quick Build (All Applications)

```bash
./build.sh
```

### Build Individual Applications

```bash
cd build

# Manager GUI only
make shadps4-manager-gui -j$(nproc)

# CLI extractor only
make shadps4-pkg-extractor -j$(nproc)

# Unlock generator only
make shadps4-unlock-code-generator -j$(nproc)
```

### Clean Build

```bash
./scripts/clean.sh
./build.sh
```

