## 🎯 Usage Examples

### Manager GUI

```bash
# Launch application
./build/bin/shadps4-manager-gui

# Configure paths in Settings tab
# Scan downloads folder for PKG files
# Install games with one click
```

### CLI Extractor

```bash
# Extract a single PKG
./build/bin/shadps4-pkg-extractor game.pkg /output/dir

# Extract with verbose output
./build/bin/shadps4-pkg-extractor game.pkg /output/dir --verbose

# Batch extract all PKGs
for pkg in *.pkg; do
    ./build/bin/shadps4-pkg-extractor "$pkg" "/output/$(basename "$pkg" .pkg)"
done
```

### Unlock Generator (Admins Only)

```bash
# Launch generator
./build/bin/shadps4-unlock-code-generator

# 1. Enter customer's System ID
# 2. Enter customer's email
# 3. Click "Generate Unlock Code"
# 4. Copy code and send to customer
```

